S.FORM: Borut Pahor I 1963 a miheca saka 11 folad saka 2 a romi'ad masofoc ci Borut Pahor, malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Slovenia anini i ci Borut Pahor, patirengan a romi'ad i 2012 a miheca saka 12 folad saka 22 a romi'ad. kasofocan a loma' 出生家庭 lalamod 配偶 salikaka 兄弟姐妹 natayalan 事蹟 pitooran 宗教
